{"tid":1971022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾出聲支持香港抗爭，日本APA飯店願意借出5千間房，接納日本輕症患者","createTime":"2020-04-13T14:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T17:40:54.000Z","uid":75656,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"851f1e8c89a043ad17fad6b573437f4e75b0306f","tid":1971022,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"日本厚生勞働省（相當於國內衛福部與勞動部結合）日前表示為避免醫療系統超出負荷，決定讓武漢肺炎（COVID-19）輕症患者於酒店或家中隔離，藉以減輕醫療系統負荷。兩家國人熟悉的日本旅館業者東橫Inn以及APA酒店均點頭同意，尤其是一向被日本民眾視為特立獨行的APA女總裁元谷芙美子，還霸氣喊出願意接納全部輕症患者，瞬間讓日本民眾高度讚賞，更稱APA酒店為「愛國飯店」。<br />\n<br />\n日本武漢肺炎確診人數累計已直逼7000大關，醫療系統不堪負荷，因此日本政府從4月7日起開始，將輕症患者和無症狀感染者轉移至酒店等住宿設施，對於轉移、餐食、隔離等費用，將用公費支付。<br />\n<br />\n而率先同意接納輕症患者的防疫旅館，正是國人所熟悉的商務旅館龍頭：東橫Inn以及APA酒店，7日首日在東京中央區的「東橫INN新大橋前」已經有10名患者入住，同意讓輕症患者入住的飯店，則不接受其他旅客住宿，以免交叉感染。<br />\n<br />\n在這次徵召行動中，東橫INN借出了4棟飯店；此外，APA 酒店的社長元谷芙美子更霸氣表明，雖然政府目前只要跟他們借1棟，但是如果有需要的話，全東京3000間、大阪1500間、名古屋350間，共計5000間房間都可以借！而且從事醫療的入住可以得到半價優惠！同時也保證一定會保護員工安全，共同面對武漢肺炎的國難！<br />\n<br />\n消息一出，日本民眾與網友均對這一向被認為特立獨行的女總裁豎起大拇指，紛紛稱讚APA是「愛國飯店」。<br />\n<br />\n過去，APA酒店社長元谷芙美子經常被拿來當作揶揄對象，主要是這位女總裁不顧外界眼光，堅持在廣告或者自家飯店商品或用品上大大的掛上她的玉照，且對外總是帶著招牌大帽子、穿短裙、以及畫上鮮豔的眼影，特別顯得令人印象深刻。同時2017年間更大剌剌在酒店放上右翼書籍，不承認南京大屠殺，遭到中國旅客抵制。<br />\n<br />\n這次網友在推特上以及網路上不再揶揄她，也不拿她當搞笑橋段了，而是紛紛大讚其作為，把她當作是這次武漢肺炎的救世主，更有網友到APA酒店粉絲專頁留言感謝APA酒店集團對這次疫情的付出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2059532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2059532&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B85Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=a8cac01c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2059532</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPx6VCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPx6VCY.jpg&h=345ff9b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAPA Hotel 支持香港抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697116</a><br />\n<br />\n日本 APA Hotel 支持香港抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697432</a>"},{"pid":"bd977da1d9739bff4af81a19d3962f0d31bbe7cf","tid":1971022,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8499bb29708e4674afcc6c2794862b7beb9e1b","tid":1971022,"uid":261964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:55:22.000Z","msg":"Support <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去日本只住APA"},{"pid":"8a5833d66dbfb83a82ba01ee47c1ab5edf870bb3","tid":1971022,"uid":8799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"APA 幾好住 係細啲 但電視大到半張床咁"},{"pid":"99e48dc631db64f26c075079f9ef12b16c232eef","tid":1971022,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:20:22.000Z","msg":"義氣仔女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d3560b00df551639fc20bff6bc7bb1e1cc258b","tid":1971022,"uid":50670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T16:29:38.000Z","msg":"三百幾蚊間房，毒遊一流"},{"pid":"b3b0860a3ec1be5bfdbc9ddbbb5c286dd305af63","tid":1971022,"uid":151074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"相比今時今日支支對世界對香港今世人嘅暴行，不承認南京大屠殺真係不值一提。支那多年來殺人、虐待弱者嘅行為，唔會輸俾皇軍。"},{"pid":"adbac3c2d123d450b7582c2d4c797b43d0e8c0ca","tid":1971022,"uid":132896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b3b0860a3ec1be5bfdbc9ddbbb5c286dd305af63","tid":1971022,"uid":151074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"相比今時今日支支對世界對香港今世人嘅暴行，不承認南京大屠殺真係不值一提。支那多年來殺人、虐待弱者嘅行為，唔會輸俾皇軍。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"同大躍進 三反五反 文革比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂南京屠殺都真係輸哂"},{"pid":"976c37a98c17fc07ae174da02823b1b6d8363954","tid":1971022,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T17:15:30.000Z","msg":"堅決支持日本黃酒店APA！！！"},{"pid":"93a2bba46437b915649598c0d840f88f31963f3c","tid":1971022,"uid":253608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T17:17:52.000Z","msg":"APA 好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2e18e0ef0c7060ce2bebd2ce205e31fd12c940","tid":1971022,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T17:21:12.000Z","msg":"遲啲再幫襯，一月去札幌時有訂埋早餐"},{"pid":"108efc8553d7d45ea205e7aaf8c7ef357dcb8550","tid":1971022,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T17:22:09.000Z","msg":"以後住滿住爆APA<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2cbc3e0ae62fde8067eda353d74b7bbf1d6509","tid":1971022,"uid":152104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T17:22:29.000Z","msg":"APA平平地都幾OK架"},{"pid":"d263bbb810b43b800b549ed8e84269bec2594cc4","tid":1971022,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T17:28:14.000Z","msg":"單拖最愛APA<br />\n啲嘢新淨又乾淨"},{"pid":"717b770d9cbd59ef9cdf695ef54f2856b42b8933","tid":1971022,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"APA 如果可以好似toyoko 唔洗食海鮮價就好"},{"pid":"8dba31ea67afb79a38e818254f34bc5993bfbd49","tid":1971022,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T17:30:04.000Z","msg":"每年日本之行都係住APA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a490c8385932341dd3bead1fc6635ba5ee77e83","tid":1971022,"ui